    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains exceptional mechanical health with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing both functioning within factory spec. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and suspension remain tight and performance-ready.",
